description: Provides a Security Hub custom insight resource. See the [Managing custom insights section](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/securityhub/latest/userguide/securityhub-custom-insights.html) of the AWS User Guide for more information.

tfcfnid.description: Internal identifier for tracking resource changes. Do not use.

GroupByAttribute.description: The attribute used to group the findings for the insight e.g. if an insight is grouped by `ResourceId`, then the insight produces a list of resource identifiers.

Name.description: The name of the custom insight.
